com.hazelcast.query.impl.predicates

Class AbstractPredicate<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.query.impl.predicates.AbstractPredicate<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSerializable, IdentifiedDataSerializable, Predicate<K,V>, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractIndexAwarePredicate, LikePredicate, RegexPredicate

    public abstract class AbstractPredicate<K,V>
extends Object
implements Predicate<K,V>, IdentifiedDataSerializable
    Provides base features for predicates, such as extraction and conversion of the attribute's value. It also handles apply() on MultiResult.
